Package org.lgdcloudsim.conflicthandler

Interface ConflictHandler

All Superinterfaces:
DatacenterEntity
All Known Implementing Classes:
ConflictHandlerSimple
public interface ConflictHandler extends DatacenterEntity
An interface to be implemented by each class that represents a resource allocator. When multiple Instances are assigned to the same host at the same time, it is necessary to select which Instances are placed on the host and which are not placed on the host through it.
Since:
LGDCloudSim 1.0
Author:
Anonymous
